    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient predictive accuracy (maximum RHI deviation 11.8%) against FDA pump experimental data across the full CPB operating envelope. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at the worst-case operating condition. The credibility evidence package supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
